<button type="button" class="collapsible large" style="margin-top:4.5px;"><span style="width: 40%; margin-right: 10%;margin-top: 100%;">What is SharePod?</span>   <span style="float: right;margin-bottom: 0.5%;"><img src="/images/login/down.png" style="width: 5vh;height: 20%;"></span></button>
<div class="content large">
  <p>SharePod is a web based application which can be used by your friends, family or colleagues, to let you know that they require some particular items,products or groceries which they need to buy, and so that you can buy those items for them when you visit the supermarket or store yourself, and vice versa. </p>
</div>
<br>
<button type="button" class="collapsible large" style="margin-top:4.5px;"><span style="width: 40%; margin-right: 10%;margin-top: 100%;">How is SharePod useful for me?</span>   <span style="float: right;margin-bottom: 0.5%;"><img src="/images/login/down.png" style="width: 5vh;height: 20%;"></span></button>
<div class="content large">
  <p>Have you ever been in a situation where you had to ask your friend or family member or even your neighbour for a favour as to buy you some items from the grocery store or supermarket, since they were already going there and it would save you both time and fuel to not go there or maybe just because you're too lazy . Or maybe you could have been in the other person's shoes, with an intent of helping them out and thinking that it would be really nice if you could buy some items for them as well.
Well, if you have been in such a situation, then SharePod is a must try web app for you!</p>
</div>
<br>
<button type="button" class="collapsible large" style="margin-top: 4.5px;"><span style="width: 40%; margin-right: 10%;margin-top: 100%;">How do I use SharePod?</span>   <span style="float: right;margin-bottom: 0.5%;"><img src="/images/login/down.png" style="width: 5vh;height: 20%;"></span></button>
<div class="content large">
  <p>You need to simply sign up by filling in some basic information about yourself, create a room by using your own custom room ID and password as per you wish, share those ID and password with your friends by any convenient means and voila, you're good to go!
For further detailed explanation, you can see our ‘How to Use’ page which contains step by step instructions on our web app usage.</p>
</div>
